Resolução¶

Da direita para a esquerda:

  • $? = A \times B$
  • $? = B \times A$
  • $? = A \times B$

In [1]:
p1 = fst
p2 = snd
split f g x = (f x, g x)

-- type checking

:t split p2 p1
:t split p2 p1 . split p2 p1

-- testing with (x,y) = (2,3)

((split p2 p1) . (split p2 p1)) (2,3) == id (2,3)
split p2 p1 :: forall b1 b2. (b1, b2) -> (b2, b1)
split p2 p1 . split p2 p1 :: forall b1 b2. (b1, b2) -> (b1, b2) 
True
In [3]:
-- applying

split p2 p1 . split p2 p1 $ (2,3)

(2,3)
